{"tid":600083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前警員呃住宿舍5年 官指服務警隊「無功都有勞」判服務令","createTime":"2018-03-21T04:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T07:42:10.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8dca8e101183c3740ac5137534f13dad615ee5c6","tid":600083,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"無功都有勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n警員隱瞞已離婚以霸佔已婚宿舍5年，前妻於前年向警方發告密信踢爆事件。現已離開警隊的前警員早前承認欺詐罪，還柙至今判刑。他親自求情稱已知錯及深感後悔，承諾以分期形式每月向警隊還款5,000元清還欠租。裁判官指被告服務警隊多年「無功都有勞」，考慮他並非早有預謀犯案及已扣押兩周，今判被告接受100小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n案情指被告鍾志堅（43歲）1998年結婚，2001年入住順利紀律部隊已婚宿舍，至2011年6月9日家事法庭頒下令離婚，至其上司於2016年6月為他撰寫年度報告，他仍沒有依警隊規定申報婚姻狀況已改變，同年9月被告請辭，10月搬離宿舍，一個月後警方收到前妻告密，事件始曝光。<br />\n<br />\n被告去年1月正式離職，計及由2011年6月9日至2016年10月10日，因被告虛報婚姻狀況令政府損失租金收入59.2萬元。被告於今年1月被捕時，於警誡下保持緘默，他曾求情指稱因離婚而心情差劣，又指找不到住處才一時愚蠢下犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180321/57975055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180321%2F57975055&d=5gUHD5hnZIOw1Z4EuMo5TJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9f57299c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180321%2F57975055&h=04c8c900\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180321/57975055</a>"},{"pid":"00c21ccc185acb1bb532019014a0770fa1ee91de","tid":600083,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"並非早有預謀犯案?<br />\n<br />\nnick young"},{"pid":"007b1c1b0ab82758bd92ce83eb3cec9157fcdc2f","tid":600083,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1f39fe1b39eb089438290355a7e8fb0b39b2426","tid":600083,"uid":726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"咁都係減刑理由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d72e27fdb9991c1c16a91cbf550a9a851443883","tid":600083,"uid":123304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛出糧俾你?"},{"pid":"0be267c38d9bf0b00d405600573a7cef48d587c9","tid":600083,"uid":176698,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"無功都有勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢做義工？無出糧？ 如果係低下階層犯事，就即刻送人入去坐。個個都係無功都有勞，我地比佢地更勞。反而佢唔係知法犯法？"},{"pid":"24e8544e3d20383e60d73e934d8cbd06e382cdd9","tid":600083,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"損失租金收入59.2萬元<br />\n以分期形式每月向警隊還款5,000元清還欠租<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪要還 118個月, 即係 9.8年?"},{"pid":"9b49ef98cce8f4403191bd2997d7f1e55c62359e","tid":600083,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"屌，無跟案例，you&rsquo;re well paid"},{"pid":"ac1aea453d9a7cf5dc8ed6fb7c5d9005a3305727","tid":600083,"uid":127611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"前妻好波"},{"pid":"343e3d7ed0e02a65b31cd53064ad9816f75df8be","tid":600083,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"古有知法犯法，罪加一等<br />\n今有知法犯法，無功有勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81ed9865a36f852c18baef365c6c5fde2a1da5e","tid":600083,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"咁個撚個虧空公款都可以用無功都有勞啦！"},{"pid":"c8a20e7abf7685954d6dd2404f27f04cd256b905","tid":600083,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩勞？<br />\n如果佢地有<br />\n全世界有番工嘅人都有囉"},{"pid":"47b5443d50e808bbde0a9d3fae12058fa6002cbe","tid":600083,"uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:41:30.000Z","msg":"你老母俾人強姦，用強姦犯都有出力架。<br />\n<br />\n咁又算唔算冇功都有勞？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，唔洗出力呀？"},{"pid":"343406c80f960966ac6537ead0b3b7c1e333fe34","tid":600083,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"並非早有預謀犯案<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1263c2420e1023c65415d82fbe59b62b8980ec9b","tid":600083,"uid":35648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"又邊個官"},{"pid":"75ca06390aa5d3ab3c5e2a4029a3f5c5e9946a15","tid":600083,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"講到做義工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fc0275184f7cda857176cf0b2d57825258b73a","tid":600083,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"無功都有勞？？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nYOU ARE WELL PAID FOR IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"517645e8983e4b397290f3c57850fb08273c1fff","tid":600083,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"以為公職人員犯法都可以話無功都有勞減輕懲罰<br />\n貪曾識做啦？"},{"pid":"b417f372c86ff8afe0befe9576358bad894dcbb0","tid":600083,"uid":63520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"